1. What is Deep Learning? Interview Definition  Deep Learning (DL) is a subset of Machine Learning (ML) that uses Artificial Neural Networks (ANNs) with multiple hidden layers to automatically learn complex patterns from large amounts of data.  Simple Definition  Machine Learning me hum features manually dete hain.  Deep Learning me computer khud data se features learn karta hai.  Example:  Image me cat detect karna.  ML → Shape, ears, tail manually define karne padte hain. DL → Model automatically samajh leta hai ki cat kya hoti hai. 2. Deep Learning Analysis  Deep Learning ko analyze karte hain step by step.  Component	Analysis Input	Data diya jata hai Hidden Layers	Features automatically learn karti hain Activation Function	Decide karta hai neuron fire kare ya nahi Loss Function	Error calculate karta hai Optimizer	Error ko kam karta hai Output Layer	Final prediction deta hai 3. What is "Deep"?  "Deep" ka matlab hota hai  Multiple Hidden Layers  Example  Traditional Neural Network  Input    ↓ Hidden    ↓ Output  Deep Neural Network  Input  ↓  Hidden 1  ↓  Hidden 2  ↓  Hidden 3  ↓  Hidden 4  ↓  Output  Jitni zyada hidden layers hongi, utna network "Deep" kehlata hai.  4. Why Deep Learning?  Traditional ML ki limitations  Manual Feature Engineering Complex Data handle nahi kar pata Images difficult Audio difficult Video difficult NLP difficult  Deep Learning automatically  ✔ Learns Features  ✔ Learns Patterns  ✔ Learns Relationships  5. Deep Learning Overview Artificial Intelligence (AI)          ↓  Machine Learning (ML)          ↓  Deep Learning (DL)          ↓  Neural Networks 6. Artificial Intelligence  AI ka goal hai  Machine ko intelligent banana.  Example  ChatGPT Siri Alexa Self Driving Car 7. Machine Learning  Machine data se learn karti hai.  Input  ↓  Training  ↓  Prediction  8. Deep Learning  Deep Learning  ↓  Neural Networks  ↓  Large Data  ↓  Automatic Learning  ↓  Prediction  9. Why is Deep Learning Popular? Because it works amazingly on  Images  Videos  Voice  Text  Translation  Medical Images  Robotics  Self Driving Cars  Generative AI  10. Real Life Examples Face Unlock  Image  ↓  CNN  ↓  Face Recognition  Google Translate  Sentence  ↓  Transformer  ↓  Translation  ChatGPT  Question  ↓  Transformer  ↓  Answer  Netflix  User History  ↓  Deep Learning  ↓  Movie Recommendation  11. Deep Learning Workflow Collect Data  ↓  Preprocess Data  ↓  Train Model  ↓  Calculate Error  ↓  Update Weights  ↓  Repeat  ↓  Model Ready  ↓  Prediction 12. Components of Deep Learning (1) Dataset  Model ko sikhane ke liye data.  Example  10000 Cat Images  10000 Dog Images  (2) Input Layer  Yahi se data network me enter hota hai.  Image  ↓  Pixels  ↓  Input Layer  (3) Hidden Layers  Sabse important part.  Yahi learning hoti hai.  Example  Image  ↓  Edges  ↓  Shapes  ↓  Eyes  ↓  Nose  ↓  Face  ↓  Cat  Har hidden layer different feature learn karti hai.  (4) Neuron  Neural Network ka smallest unit.  Neuron  Input  ↓  Calculation  ↓  Activation  ↓  Output  (5) Weights  Har connection ki importance.  Large Weight  ↓  More Importance  Small Weight  ↓  Less Importance  (6) Bias  Extra adjustable value.  Prediction improve karta hai.  Formula  Output = Weight × Input + Bias (7) Activation Function  Neuron ko decide karna hota hai  Output bhejna hai ya nahi.  Popular  ReLU Sigmoid Tanh Softmax (8) Loss Function  Prediction kitni galat hai.  Example  Actual = Dog  Prediction = Cat  ↓  Loss High  (9) Optimizer  Loss ko reduce karta hai.  Popular  Gradient Descent Adam RMSProp (10) Epoch  Pure dataset ka  1 complete training cycle.  100 Epoch  ↓  Dataset 100 baar train hua.  (11) Batch  Entire dataset ka chhota part.  Example  10000 Images  Batch Size = 100  To  100 batches banenge.  (12) Forward Propagation  Input  ↓  Prediction  (13) Backpropagation  Prediction Error  ↓  Weights Update  ↓  Model Improve  13. Deep Learning Types ANN  Artificial Neural Network  Best For  Tabular Data CNN  Convolutional Neural Network  Best For  Images Face Detection Medical Images RNN  Recurrent Neural Network  Best For  Sequential Data Text Time Series LSTM  Long Short-Term Memory  Best For  Long Text Speech Time Series Transformer  Best For  ChatGPT Gemini Claude Translation LLM
